Snag — media downloader

Snag is a fork of cobalt by imput (https://github.com/imputnet/cobalt).
The original cobalt project is licensed under multiple licenses across
its modules:

  - cobalt API server: AGPL-3.0
  - cobalt API client SDK: MIT
  - cobalt web frontend: CC-BY-NC-SA 4.0 (Creative Commons,
    Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike)

Snag retains the AGPL-3.0 license for the API server and packages
that were inherited from cobalt under that license.

Snag does NOT redistribute or build upon cobalt's CC-BY-NC-SA 4.0
web frontend. The Snag web frontend is an independent SvelteKit
implementation written from scratch under the AGPL-3.0 license.

The cobalt mascot ("meowbalt") and associated artwork are not
under any open license; they belong to imput and are not included
in Snag in any form.

We are grateful to imput and the cobalt contributors for the
foundation of free, ethical media-downloading software.
